nadina bhagya ( kannada : ನಾಡಿನ ಭಾಗ ಯ ) is a 1970 indian kannada film , directed by r. nagendra rao and produced by s narayanappa and n narasimharaju . the film stars rajkumar in guest appearance , r. nagendra rao , r. n. sudarshan and t. r. narasimharaju in lead roles . the film had musical score by r. rathnam .